strings.Value: "How does it feel to be chieftain?"
"Warmest greetings! You're always a welcome {d|c41 Chief Gwart}guest{/d} of the tribe."

"It isn't easy, I must confess. Many tribesmen claim I'm too young to lead. Every day, I have to prove to the tribe that I'm worthy of this position. But {g|Gorum}Gorum{/g} doesn't abandon me. Mark my words â€” soon, their doubts will disappear!"
"Armag dealt us a heavy blow. We're trying to recover, restore our strength... But truth be told, it will take a long time for us to return to what we once were."
